description: Unlock the Power of Digital Finance with Swap. Seamlessly convert tokens and embrace a user-friendly tool for the future of finance. name: DemoWebon
description: For developers, DemoWebon is an invaluable resource. It's designed to provide a dedicated environment for developing Nomo WebOns and comes complete with tutorials, readily available on dev.nomo.app. This WebOn serves as an interactive showcase of various features that can be integrated into your custom WebOns. This includes capabilities like signing transactions through provided npm packages, interacting with the chat, sending assets, scanning QR codes, and adding custom tokens.

name: TVOTE
description:
Introducing TVOTE, a cutting-edge vote technology built on smart contracts. With TVOTE, the future of secure and transparent voting is here. Through blockchain technology, TVOTE ensures the integrity of every vote, eliminating the risk of fraud or manipulation.

Say goodbye to long lines and paper ballots; TVOTE allows for convenient and efficient digital voting from the comfort of your device. Each vote is recorded immutably on the blockchain, making results tamper-proof and instantly accessible.

TVOTE also enhances inclusivity, enabling remote voting for those unable to physically attend. Plus, it's eco-friendly, reducing the need for paper-based systems. Embrace the future of democratic participation with TVOTE, where every voice counts, and trust in the voting process is fully restored.
